## 1. Summary
The chat primarily revolves around the upcoming migration of AI16Z to ElizaOS tokens. Community members are seeking information about the migration timeline and process. A team member (Kenk) confirms that the migration is not yet live and directs users to monitor the official Mirror page for updates. There's discussion about preparing for the migration by setting up CMC and Coingecko pages in advance and coordinating with CEXs. Dr. Neuro confirms the migration will occur in October. Some users express concern about token price movements, while others remain optimistic about the long-term prospects. The new token contract address is not yet available as the migration hasn't launched.
